## Content Publishing — human-in-the-loop decision points
## Agent writes an article, then requests human approval before publishing.

### Request an article
POST http://localhost:9000/publishing
Content-Type: application/json

{"topic": "The future of renewable energy in urban environments"}

### Check status — look for pendingQuestion when awaiting approval
GET http://localhost:9000/publishing/{{id}}

### Approve publication
POST http://localhost:9000/publishing/{{id}}/approve

### Reject with feedback (agent will revise)
POST http://localhost:9000/publishing/{{id}}/reject
Content-Type: application/json

{"reason": "The article needs more concrete examples and data points"}
